body:
Last night I was playing ranked with a few friends, as my turn came about to select a champion, I was hovered over {{champion:245}} . While I was discussing picks, I decided to switch to {{champion:61}}  with 3 seconds remaining. I quickly switched and locked in my pick, but to my dismay the client simply decided to kick me out of the champion select and directly back to the lobby. 
Perhaps a good fix would be to create an autolock function for the last 5 seconds of the champ select.
3LP loss isn&#039;t that bad, but that means a potential extra game I have to play to get into promos. {{item:3070}}
